{"tid":1896050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據悉本港今早再多一名24歲男子初步確診 未曾到過佛堂 但其母及大姨曾到過佛堂並確診","createTime":"2020-02-25T01:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T05:49:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":117,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"ad75e7be023c781d4a4044684c5941506eff8928","tid":1896050,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:57:58.000Z","msg":"可致命的武漢肺炎疫情在本港未受控，昨日（24日）增至81宗確診，其中6宗與北角福慧精舍佛堂相關。昨日另有2宗初步確診，其中1宗都牽涉佛堂。據悉，本港今早再多一宗初步確診，患者是24歲男子，正在律敦治醫院留醫，等待衞生防護中心覆檢。他未曾到過福慧精舍佛堂，但其母親是曾到佛堂、昨晚初步確診的55歲女子；其57歲大姨更是昨日衞生防護中心公佈的確診個案。若該男子最終確診，將成為首位未曾到過佛堂、但其確診家人曾到訪的個案，顯示佛堂或有二代傳播。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200225/T4NASE5UIDURDHQXRLO3AL6O2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FT4NASE5UIDURDHQXRLO3AL6O2E%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=8ba272f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FT4NASE5UIDURDHQXRLO3AL6O2E%2F&h=ef771c7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200225/T4NASE5UIDURDHQXRLO3AL6O2E/</a>"},{"pid":"3e39e76439fb3f113fdb6d68fecef5a2af8914a5","tid":1896050,"uid":258566,"like":10,"dislike":21,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aa0f0325ed9e9caf88daa8938270a973761d243","tid":1896050,"uid":212626,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"計埋初步確診<br />\n暫時累計84宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44422d762bdd28b78276677645d3e06caf5ff62","tid":1896050,"uid":6845,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3e39e76439fb3f113fdb6d68fecef5a2af8914a5","tid":1896050,"uid":258566,"like":10,"dislike":21,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"係就應該一早上左黎 或者個ac 唔方便開post 咁就精彩了"},{"pid":"0d144ec6cc77d7dd2e65215da073f0d049743c43","tid